Package: ridbAPI
Title: Query the Recreation Information Database API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jacob",
           family = "Bradt",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jtbradt@gmail.com")
Description: This package provides a set of R wrapper functions used to bulk extract data
    from the Recreation Information Database (RIDB) API, which is part of the Recreation
    One Stop (Rec1Stop) project. The package supports queries to all API endpoints as of
    v1.0 of the RIDB API. For additional information on the RIDB API, see 
    https://ridb.recreation.gov/
License: `use_mit_license()`
